title: Hour 2: Stanky Yankees
description:
Stephen A. and Mad Dog get into it over Aaron Rodgers recent comments on the Packers WRs. Plus they debate if its time to panic for the Yankees. Later is it Super Bowl or Bust for the Bills? Sam Acho thinks so. Plus Stephen A. doesn't want to hear anything about the Cowboys winning the NFC East.
